  "Description": {
    "English": "Naturally transform your appearance via the application of a flesh-hungry parasite. This living being partially fuses with the brainstem of its host, sealing their symbiosis.<br><br>Cautiously transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "你可以应用一种嗜肉的寄生虫来自然地改变你的外观。这种生物会与宿主的脑干部分融合以稳固共生关系。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>中改变你套装的外观，改变时请谨慎小心。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "利用吃肉的寄生蟲，自然改變你的外貌。本活體有一部分會與宿主的腦幹結合，建立起永久的共生關係。<br><br>保持小心，在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
